CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper September 25, 1943, pg. 19, reads: "Joe Louis Shows a Boxing Soldier How to Block a Punch; Spars with Nicholson - Thousands of soldiers got the thrill of their lives last Monday at Shenango when Heavyweight Champion Joe Louis appeared there with his troupe of boxers... At the right: Louis back in action with Sparring Partner George Nicholson. - U. S. Army and Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Copy of a photograph of boxer Joe Louis and sparring partner George Nicholson in ring at Shenango Veteran's Hospital
